response.original_title: Pro Wrestling Illustrated presents Lords of the Ring: Superstars & Superbouts
response.overview: A collection of some of the greatest wrestling moments of the 70's and 80's. Highlights include Ric Flair's second world title win, Kerry VonErich's title win, a battle between the VonErichs and the Fabulous Freebirds, and a dog collar match between Roddy Piper and Greg Valentine. Hosted by Bill Apter and Gordon Solie.
response.tagline: The Road Warriors, "Nature Boy" Ric Flair, Jerry "The King" Lawler, Dusty Rhodes, "Rowdy" Roddy Piper, Gorgeous George and much much more!
response.title: Pro Wrestling Illustrated presents Lords of the Ring: Superstars & Superbouts
